snippet: Officials at Auburn have announced that the iconic oak trees at Toomer’s Corner will be removed.
abstract: Officials at Auburn University announce that iconic oak trees at Toomer’s Corner will be removed; say trees are unlikely to survive despite efforts to save them after they were poisoned with powerful herbicide.
lead_paragraph: Officials at Auburn have announced that the iconic oak trees at Toomer’s Corner will be removed.

headline.main: Trees at Auburn Will Be Removed
